comments: Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Beal (WAS) during the drive but does not affect his SQBR.
Bridges (CHA) extends his hand into Wagner's (WAS) back and affects his shot near the rim.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Smith's (WAS) path.
Wagner (WAS) extends his arm and makes contact with Graham's (CHA) body during the driving shot attempt.
After Beal (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball, he makes incidental leg to leg contact with Rozier (CHA).
Mahinmi (WAS) holds Zeller (CHA) off-ball and affects his FOM.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Smith's (WAS) path.
Mahinmi (WAS) establishes legal defensive position outside the RA and absorbs the contact from Washington (CHA) during his driving shot attempt.
Mahinmi (WAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bridges' (CHA) path.
Bartans (WAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bridges' (CHA) path.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Mahinmi (WAS) off-ball.
Mahinmi (WAS) fails to clear the lane within three seconds.
Mahinmi (WAS) extends an arm to Rozier's (CHA) front during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Hachimura (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path.
Beal (WAS) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) as he starts his drive.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests the shot attempt by Bertans (WAS).
Hachimura (WAS) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
